    "AutoSAM [169] embedded an auxiliary prompt encoder to generate a surrogate prompt via the features of the input images, eliminating the manual prompts.",
    "PUNETR [184] studied the prompt tuning method which embeds some learnable prompt tokens into the pre-trained networks to adapt the prompt for medical images.",
